        "quote": "It's so good to have you back. I was just watching our first episode, which we did two and a half years ago. I was watching it, and I was both shocked and not shocked that we barely talked about AI. The episode was called How to Measure and Improve Developer Productivity, and we got to AI barely like an hour in and we're just like, \"Hmm, I wonder what's going to happen with AI and productivity.\" Does that just blow your mind?",
