        "speaker": "Melissa Perri",
        "timestamp": "00:00:03",
        "quote": "Scaled Agile Framework came out of the desire to figure out how do we scale Scrum and different processes. I do not recommend using SAFe. Every single person I have talked to who likes SAFe, found success with SAFe, they ended up ripping it up and making it into something else.",
