        "speaker": "I really am. Yeah. And I actually want to thank Riley too. I got to know Riley when I was at oDesk first as a research scientist, and then I directed their data science team. This is way back in 2012, and I was looking around for people who are experts on how we think about data and marketplaces, and Riley Newman came up and so I invited him to come talk to us at oDesk, and we've stayed in touch since then.",
        "timestamp": "00:05:26",
        "quote": "Those were early days of where this industry was, and I've had a kind of lengthy career now thinking about those kinds of problems. So I'm pretty excited to talk about it with you.",
