        "quote": "Yeah, exactly. And they were like, \"Hey, this is bad, you have to stop doing this. But can we hire you to solve the problem?\" And so what started off as me running projects for local bars in Vancouver, or clothing stores, or whatever it was. Turned into me landing early stage Uber as a client, and really graduating us from competent professionals to leaders in our sector. And so it was a fascinating project, and we worked with Uber for 10 years.",
