        "timestamp": "00:05:23",
        "quote": "Because we're able to exit this deal that didn't work out and go into launching Dev Mode and really pushing on how do we expand our platform in a big way. It's been I think just further acceleration of pace from there. I'm really proud of the team for how they handled that and also how they're in focus now, and it's a real honor to be on this team.",
